# Local secrets (OPENROUTER_API_KEY etc.) auto-loaded by loadPolicy — NEVER commit a key.
.council.env
# Auto-apply CONSENTS live OUT OF TREE (Appendix D — consent containment): a gitignored, per-clone,
# fingerprint-bound trust file. NEVER commit it — a tracked consent would spread to clones/forks/
# PR-checkouts and let a bare `fix` auto-apply writes with no consent from that operator.
.council.local.yml
# §5 char-test transient test files + coverage dirs (created/deleted per phase; listed so a hard-crash
# residue never dirties the tree or gets picked up by tooling)
.council-chartest-*
.agents/
